law.text:
KRS 411.250 to 411.266 shall:
Apply to any claim that arises before, on, or after July 15, 2003, as the result of a construction defect, except a claim for personal injury or wrongful death, if the claim is the subject of an action commenced on or after July 15, 2003;
Prevail over any conflicting law otherwise applicable to the claim or cause of action;
Not bar or limit any claim or defense otherwise available except as otherwise provided in KRS 411.250 to 411.266; and
Not create a new theory upon which liability may be based.
